        "name": "Rivethun Devotion",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Through study, dedication, and introspection, you've learned to wield magic that affects the spirit. You gain *see the unseen* and *spirit link* as 2nd-rank divine innate spells. You can cast each of these spells once per day. If you're a master in Religion, *spirit link* is heightened to 3rd rank. If you're legendary in Religion, *spirit link* is heightened to 4th rank.",
